assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Groupe Minoteries SA processes, refines, and markets grain and food raw materials in Switzerland. It offers flour and grain products; organic flours and ready-to-use products, such as muesli, flakes, etc.; and breadcrumbs. The company was founded in 1885 and is headquartered in Granges-près-Marnand, Switzerland.
